::Dollen::

           The stasis pod DNA scanners scanned the area for a suitable
lifeform to give Dollen a beast mode.  After a suitable lifeform was found,
the bot inside, named Dollen, heard banging on the stasis pod, and someone
talking to him.  The stasis pod opened up, and Dollen stepped out.

            Dollen looked at GoldenEye.  He suddenly thought about dreams
and visions he had been having about a female bot.  The female bot he kept
having visions about was beautiful.  But, he did not know her name, or
anything.  He looked at GoldenEye again.  No.  This bot wasn't the one.  He
looked at her symbol.  Then he looked at his.  She wasn't an enemy.  She was
on his side, or so it appeared.  He had to make sure.  He looked at his
signature detector.  Yes, she was a Predacon, on his side.

                  "Ah, nice to meet you.  My name is Dollen.  I see your a
Predacon, like me," Dollen stopped, and grabbed a little thing from his arm
storage compartment.  Inside it was creamy stuff, and then Dollen put some
on his finger, and rubbed it on his Pred symbol, which was located on his
chest.  He grabbed a cloth out of his arm as well, which was odd, as you
don't see too many bots with a cloth.  He rubbed his symbol with the cloth,
and then his symbol was shiny and clean.  He put the stuff back in his
compartment.

           "Sorry about that little pause, I had to polish my symbol, to
show that I respect my title as a Predacon.  Anyway, what is your name?"
